# TypeScript Standards

- Strict mode; no `any` (use `unknown` + narrow)
- `as const` objects instead of `enum` keyword
- Explicit return types on exported domain/infra functions
- Zod schemas for all API inputs and env vars
- Named exports only (except Next.js pages/routes)
- Path aliases: `@momus/domain`, `@momus/infra`, `@momus/shared`

```typescript
// DB snake_case → TS camelCase mapping in repositories only
export interface BugBudgetRow {
  jiraKey: string;
  defectAgeDays: number | null;
}
```

Reference PRD IDs in business logic comments: `// BB-CALC-01`
